@startuml State Machine
title State Machine Diagram - GDBBackend

[*] --> IDLE

IDLE --> STARTING : launch() / start()
STARTING --> RUNNING : *running event
STARTING --> ERROR : spawn failure

RUNNING --> STOPPED : *stopped event
RUNNING --> ERROR : unexpected exit

STOPPED --> RUNNING : continue() / next() / step()
STOPPED --> IDLE : stop() / kill()

ERROR --> IDLE : stop()

@enduml
